@apiKey = -

### Places API 검색 테스트
POST https://places.googleapis.com/v1/places:searchText
Content-Type: application/json
X-Goog-Api-Key: -
X-Goog-FieldMask:places.displayName,places.businessStatus
Referer: http://localhost:3000

{
  "textQuery": "로프트",
